summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the City Treasurer to cancel the assessment levied for the improvement of Juneau Street and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, by grading and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 3356, on portion of the north 405 feet of Government Lot 1, Section 26, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, which has been deeded to the City of Seattle for street purposes.
